
__________________________________

To run cross validation using C45 or Random Forest, run the following commands below using python 2:

python2 Evaluate weatherDataAndNoOfCrimesData.csv weatherDataAndNoOfCrimesDataDomain.xml 10 0    (for 10-fold cross validation using C45)
python2 Evaluate weatherDataAndNoOfCrimesData.csv weatherDataAndNoOfCrimesDataDomain.xml 10 1    (for 10-fold cross validation using Random Forest)

arg[1] = dataset csv file
arg[2] = domain xml file
arg[3] = no of folds
arg[4] = 1 to use random forest, 0 to use c45
arg[5] OPTIONAL = restrictions file name if using c45 only 


__________________________________

To run KNN, run the following command below using python 3:

python3 knn.py weatherDataAndNoOfCrimesData.csv 30      (for KNN using a k value of 30)

arg[2] = k-value

